{"tid":2066412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撞衫不可怕系列】Red Velvet Joy＆BLACKPINK Jennie：一個Sweet一個Wild","createTime":"2020-06-16T09:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:31:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5cef3b89af74996c490310f21b47d44c86d6bec8","tid":2066412,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK Jennie＆Red Velvet Joy的穿搭風格都有不少女生去仿傚。而同一件衣服，兩位都會穿出了截然不同的味道。<br />\n<br />\nJennie和Joy２人所穿的衣服是這套Alessandra rich黃色格紋套裝，上半身是無袖方領露腰上衣，下身則是包臀短裙，完美展現了穿衣人的腰線和臀線。長髮Joy透著小女生的甜美和一絲跳脫，妝容乾淨，只突顯了紅唇，整個人如同芭比娃娃一般。<br />\n<br />\n而Jennie則加了一件同款外套，搭配白色漁網襪，頭髮梳成五五分，用兩個髮夾夾住。 妝容上則突顯了眼妝部份，輕薄的煙燻眼妝和上挑的眼線突顯了Jennie「小野貓」魅力，整體風格也更張揚，大走復古性感風。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：Joy IG、NATE」"},{"pid":"fd34033edcfa706bfae76cf0442eaa4d6ff9adba","tid":2066412,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sjM9y09svSjV2fEcb3feuA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/et/tc.koreastardaily.com/867519159787d3a07fca7cbe1950ab01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsjM9y09svSjV2fEcb3feuA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fet%2Ftc.koreastardaily.com%2F867519159787d3a07fca7cbe1950ab01&h=18221fed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37bb58a2f1e534b5a871d73f8a446b17be42f67c","tid":2066412,"uid":165368,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"我做愛jennie<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0e34eae887913af391cf0a05af988f954490aa","tid":2066412,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"點解女人咁憎撞衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24c3aaaa086c4